text: Jack Wells (3 October 1926 - 2 April 2010) was a South African gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:2010 deaths Category:South African male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of South Africa Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bloemfontein
